name: r-venneuler
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.1-3" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-venneuler
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/venneuler_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/venneuler/venneuler_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 21d3ac847350bdabf8e7b22e594683cd6f4172b724caa7c4be57dd1a082dd97e

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-rjava
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-rjava

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('venneuler')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('venneuler')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://www.rforge.net/venneuler/, http://www.cs.uic.edu/~wilkinson/
  license: MPL-1.1
  summary: Calculates and displays Venn and Euler Diagrams
  license_family: OTHER

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - brendanf
